<h6>Inline Image Versioning</h6>
<p>Like other assets you can choose to version images in the same way. This allows you to modify existing images without having
    to worry about browser caching interfering. Additionally you can take advantage of the image pipeline for additional image manipulation.
</p>
<pre>
